  <phrase title="option_threema_gateway_privatekeyfile_explain" addon_id="ThreemaGateway" version_id="1" version_string="0.1.0"><![CDATA[If you use the end-to-end encrypted mode enter the path to your private key file here. The file must be placed in <code>library/ThreemaGateway</code>.]]></phrase>
